{"tid":1376420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(請三思而後行）西環已有兩位手足落單","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:33:53.000Z","uid":73959,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee66b07364353839e16438f0966be688fde2f2e8","tid":1376420,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"嗰兩位手足企圖混入記者堆<br />\n點知班狗發現咗<br />\n打都未開始打就落單了<br />\n少一個就係少一個<br />\n<br />\n唔係分化<br />\n但確實要智取<br />\n咁樣會危害到記者人身安全<br />\n佢哋亦冇義務去保護你<br />\n<br />\n究竟中聯辦值唔值得衝<br />\n我唔比任何意見<br />\n大家諗清楚就好了<br />\n事實放在眼前就係大量畜龍set好哂場<br />\n係天橋預備好哂槍<br />\n大家自己諗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e5fe1ea1b6e7d05739de825082a798891866432","tid":1376420,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:21:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"783df2cc87263efc127585e36ae8d71ca7210e7e","tid":1376420,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a18ed9dec59348c8da5cf43982fb3c297261222","tid":1376420,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"兩個企行人路，唔夠三人唔算集結"},{"pid":"c9c8c27608fc42249f493cc5c2f7acd310355ba2","tid":1376420,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a18ed9dec59348c8da5cf43982fb3c297261222","tid":1376420,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"兩個企行人路，唔夠三人唔算集結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"無用<br />\n啲畜龍多撚到前所未見"},{"pid":"3dd804e60ed545cbc8150160b3ac2fbe66c7e7ea","tid":1376420,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:31:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c836c825e7800b03acb85b9c161fe78475f0295","tid":1376420,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score